  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0baf \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe ? \u0b9a\u0baa\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2 \u0b95\u0bc7\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbf - \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0baa\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd- \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Is the negotiation with the International Monetary Fund a failure? Question asked in the House - Prime Minister will inform the House tomorrow - Government Answer",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "The international media has reported that the discussion with the representatives of the International Monetary Fund has failed.",
        "Opposition Leader Laxman Kiriella said that the government should inform the Parliament about the truth.",
        "He said this while presenting an interlocutory question during oral question time in Parliament on Monday 04th.",
        "The government was in discussions with the International Monetary Fund. The people of the country are very much looking forward to the outcome of this discussion.",
        "We expected the government to inform Parliament about this. But no such announcement was made.",
        "We pray that the discussions with the International Monetary Fund will be successful.",
        "Because with their help, the problem faced by the people can be solved and the country can be built. After that we can do politics.",
        "Also, the international media had reported that the government's negotiations with the International Monetary Fund had failed, especially the American media.",
        "So we need to know about its true nature. He said that it is better to present a special speech in the Parliament in this regard.",
        "Responding to this, Minister Bandula Gunawardena said officials including the President, Finance Minister and Central Bank Governor were engaged in several rounds of negotiations with the International Monetary Fund team. He said the Prime Minister will inform the House on Tuesday 5th about the progress of these negotiations."
      ],
